{"id": "cka-001", "category": "cka", "subcategory": "cluster-upgrade", "rank": "C", "question": "When upgrading a kubeadm cluster, what is the correct order: upgrade kubeadm, then run which command on the control plane?", "expected_keywords": ["kubeadm upgrade apply", "v1.30", "control plane", "kubeadm"], "expected_fix_contains": "kubeadm upgrade apply", "grading": {"keywords_required": 2, "fix_required": true, "workflow_required": false}}
